abstract: >-
  A markdown-first, locally-hosted self-improving knowledge vault shared
  by three CLI AI agents (Claude Code, Codex, Gemini). Implements
  Karpathy's LLM-Wiki pattern with G-Eval LLM-as-judge crystallization
  (96.7% verdict-agreement on a 30-sample gold set), Memgraph CE 3.9 native
  vector indexing (280× speedup over numpy cosine), bge-m3 multilingual
  embeddings, and a $0 marginal-cost subagent-fanout pattern for bulk LLM
  mutations. Organized along 8 evolutionary axes (memory, recursive
  self-improvement, multi-agent orchestration, tool composition,
  crystallization, world-model, continuous evaluation, NotebookLM
  cognitive layer) with a 4-layer Constitutional safety-gate for vault
  self-modification.
